# === SHOW AFFINITY BAR IN CLASSES TAB ===
# Called from codex/hub/classes/refresh/*.mcfunction
# Args: {abbrev:"rg", y:"1.35"}
# Run as player, at player, with Adv.InMenu

# Read stage into #aff_stage ec.temp
$execute store result score #aff_stage ec.temp run scoreboard players get @s ec.affs_$(abbrev)

# Dispatch display based on stage (text_display at fixed position below artifacts)
